      "beast_baseline": "hey i'm studying for my accounting exam and i'm kinda stuck on straight-line depreciation. can u give me the formula and maybe a quick example? like if i have a machine that costs 50000 but it'll only be worth 5000 after 5 years, how do i do that?",
